TOKYO, DESEMBER 1945

00:11:03.460 --> 00:11:06.460
Awas kalau jalan, bung.

00:11:14.490 --> 00:11:17.490
Kaukah itu, Koichi?

00:11:20.410 --> 00:11:22.410
Sumiko!

00:11:22.440 --> 00:11:24.440
Bagaimana mungkin?

00:11:24.460 --> 00:11:27.460
Bukankah kau pilot Kamikaze?

