Juga kerabatmu.

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:31.400
Anak-anakku bernasib sama.

00:12:44.420 --> 00:12:46.420
"Putraku tercinta, Koichi..."

00:12:48.450 --> 00:12:51.450
