00:14:37.460 --> 00:14:39.460
Tidak?

00:14:40.480 --> 00:14:42.480
Menarik.

00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:47.400
Tolong jangan ikuti aku.

00:14:47.430 --> 00:14:49.430
Kau mau meninggalkan kami mati di jalanan?

00:14:49.450 --> 00:14:51.450
Aku tak peduli.

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:59.480
