00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:03.400
Dengar itu? Dia amat jahat dan menakutkan.

00:15:06.420 --> 00:15:08.420
Dimana suamimu?

00:15:08.450 --> 00:15:10.450
Apa dia tentara?

00:15:11.470 --> 00:15:14.470
Apa aku kelihatan punya suami?

00:15:14.500 --> 00:15:16.500
Apa?

00:15:16.520 --> 00:15:18.520
Anak siapa dia ini?

00:15:19.440 --> 00:15:22.440
Apa itu penting?
/ Tentu penting!

00:15:25.470 --> 00:15:27.470
