00:15:38.460 --> 00:15:40.460
Tidak, memang kenapa?

00:15:42.490 --> 00:15:44.490
Apa kau ini bodoh?

00:15:44.510 --> 00:15:48.410
Kau tak memenuhi syarat merawat bayi.

00:15:48.440 --> 00:15:51.440
Kau juga tak bisa meninggalkan dia.

00:15:57.460 --> 00:15:59.460
Nama?

00:16:02.480 --> 00:16:04.480
"Akiko"

00:16:04.510 --> 00:16:06.510
Bukan, maksudku namamu.

00:16:09.430 --> 00:16:11.430
Noriko.

00:16:13.460 --> 00:16:17.460
Mengapa kau berpakaian kayak gelandangan?
Sengaja?

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:20.480
Aku bukan pelacur.

00:16:20.500 --> 00:16:22.500
Jangan terlihat hina.

00:16:23.430 --> 00:16:26.430
Bagaimanapun kau mesti bertahan hidup.
Siapa yang bisa menyalahkanmu?

00:16:32.450 --> 00:16:34.450
Bagaimana keluargamu?

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:44.480
"Haru Shikishima"  "Eiichiro Shikishima"

00:16:44.500 --> 00:16:46.500
Orangtuamu?

00:16:49.420 --> 00:16:51.420
Ya.

00:16:52.450 --> 00:16:55.450
Mereka tewas dalam serangan udara.

00:16:59.470 --> 00:17:02.470
Kalau begitu kau dan aku nasibnya sama.

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:22.400
Apa?

00:17:22.420 --> 00:17:24.420
Tidak, kau jangan...

00:17:25.440 --> 00:17:27.440
menginap...

00:17:40.470 --> 00:17:42.470
Hey!

00:17:44.490 --> 00:17:46.490
Bagaimana ceritanya?

00:17:47.420 --> 00:17:50.420
Apa maksudmu?
/ Jangan pura-pura bloon.

00:17:50.440 --> 00:17:53.440
Ibu dan anak yang kau bawa itu.

00:17:53.460 --> 00:17:56.460
Kau kira dirimu orang suci?

00:17:56.490 --> 00:17:57.490
Tidak.

00:17:57.510 --> 00:18:00.410
Mereka muncul begitu saja.

00:18:00.440 --> 00:18:03.440
Kalau mereka menginap,
kau yang ngajak.

00:18:07.460 --> 00:18:10.460
Sudah agak telat berlagak pahlawan.

00:18:11.480 --> 00:18:15.480
Sertakan aku.
